Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 10
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 56
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: rom the publisher: "In New Domino City, the hottest game in town is the Turbo Duel"
Title: YU-GI-OH 5D'S, VOL. 4
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo

Description: Rin Okumura joins an exorcist academy in order to control his inner demon. Will his classmates find out about his satanic bloodline?
Title: BLUE EXORCIST, VOL. 9
Author: Kazue Kato

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 24
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Welcome to Academy City, which teems with psychics. One of them is Mikoto Misaka, who investigates the dark side of things.
Title: A CERTAIN SCIENTIFIC RAILGUN, VOL. 7
Author: Kazuma Kamachi

Description: This new, expanded edition delves deeper into the story of Amuro Ray, a teenage mechanic, and an  experimental defense suit who are in the middle of a space war.
Title: MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM: THE ORIGIN, VOL. 1
Author: Yoshikazu Yasuhiko and Hajime Yatate
Contributor: by Yoshikazu Yasuhiko and Hajime Yatate

Description: Princess Nakaba and Prince Caesar are married to keep peace between warring countries. Will they learn to love each other?
Title: DAWN OF THE ARCANA, VOL. 9
Author: Rei Toma

Description: Staz is a vampire obsessed with Japanese culture. When a young Japanese girl he befriends suddenly dies, Staz vows to restore her, especially since it will give him a chance to walk among humans.
Title: BLOOD LAD, VOL. 2
Author: Yuuki Kodama

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.”
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 66
Author: Eiichiro Oda
